      • paginate

        public void paginate(IMXStore store,
                     java.lang.String roomId,
                     java.lang.String token,
                     EventTimeline.Direction direction,
                     ApiCallback<TokensChunkResponse<Event>> callback)
        Request messages than the given token. These will come from storage if available, from the server otherwise.
        Parameters:
        store - the store to use
        roomId - the room id
        token - the token to go back from. Null to start from live.
        direction - the pagination direction
        callback - the onComplete callback

                                     int paginationCount,
                                     ApiCallback<TokensChunkResponse<Event>> callback)
        Request events to the server. The local cache is not used. The events will not be saved in the local storage.
        Parameters:
        roomId - the room id
        token - the token to go back from.
        paginationCount - the number of events to retrieve.
        callback - the onComplete callback
